---
title: White Bean Shakshouka with coriander and crumbled goat's cheese
description: This recipe is a new take on a classic shakshouka. Though it contains the traditional elements of a rich tomato-based sauce and gently simmered eggs, it also has unexpected additions such as lime juice, warmed tortillas and Central American spices.
